{"tid":1143634,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拎條飛機王小花同大賽王牙朗比真係得啖笑","createTime":"2019-05-07T20:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T22:40:26.000Z","uid":134486,"like":36,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5b115060cfa8202aea8b8602a9e180eb883ef9","tid":1143634,"uid":134486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T20:55:38.000Z","msg":"小花次次逆境波都無料 對住啲西甲廢料1扭5就吹到史上第一<br />\n牙朗今季新轉隊 16強入3粒carry 8強出局但都叫包辦入波<br />\n加上老化祖畀阿積士逼到跟唔到 得牙朗一個肯逼 <br />\n第一季轉會踢到咁輸左 疤狗都可以抽足成個月 長期大量狗疤精液post<br />\n好似唔記得人地對上3年3歐聯1歐國咁<br />\n<br />\n小花對羅馬 首回合4:1 次回合0:3 乜都做唔到<br />\n牙朗對祖 首回合3:0 次回合畀人0:3 都強行carry 絕殺晉級<br />\n<br />\n歐國決賽畀人收山腳傷出<br />\n唔抵得人地贏到 抽到而家<br />\n好啦畀你冇傷踢左3場決賽 <br />\n1場WC 2場美洲盃<br />\n你踢足全場又做過乜??<br />\n十二碼飛機定炒單刀定完場前一腳射畀上帝??<br />\n班疤狗仔仲要吹到愛小花先係愛足球<br />\n計我話你玩花式扭波咁叻 不如去做施寶盛二世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd67bf4a6058a0b9bcb52223289bbcefaee3a9f","tid":1143634,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T22:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd357c07c74349d382b0a6a81ae1a536dfd9c466","tid":1143634,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T2